                <p class='subPar'>Mary’s WAY® is a woman’s event which strives to deepen our Catholic faith by uniting souls more closely to
                    Jesus Christ.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
            <div class='thirdPic'>
                <img class='thirdImage' src='./images/handRosary.jpg'>
