                <p class='subPar'>Find a parish near you and join us in honoring Mary’s Virtues and Obedience to God.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-4 col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4">
            <div class='thirdPic'>
                <img class='thirdImage' src='./images/praying.jpg'>
